snippet: Coca-Cola Co may have annual profits of about $9.3 billion, but that princely sum could fall short of what the world's largest soda maker needs to tempt would-be franchisees into taking over more of its regional bottling operations....

headline.print_headline: Coke Yearns for Higher Margins to Tempt Franchisees
headline.main: Coke Yearns for Higher Margins to Tempt Franchisees

lead_paragraph: Coca-Cola Co may have annual profits of about $9.3 billion, but that princely sum could fall short of what the world's largest soda maker needs to tempt would-be franchisees into taking over more of its regional bottling operations.
